## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **CGRP mAb era 2018-2019** = paradigm shift. erenumab (Aimovig 2018 first CGRP-R mAb) + fremanezumab (Ajovy 2018) + galcanezumab (Emgality 2018) + eptinezumab (Vyepti 2020 IV) — receptor-vs-ligand 두 strategy 동시 FDA. 30년 만에 migraine prevention 첫 disease-specific mAb. quantum-VQE 의 CGRP-RAMP1 PPI 가 직접 fit.
2. **gepant era 2019-2024** = small-molecule oral CGRP-R antagonist 재부활. 1세대 telcagepant 간독성 후 2세대 rimegepant (Nurtec ODT 2020 acute + prevention dual) + ubrogepant (Ubrelvy 2019 acute) + atogepant (Qulipta 2021 prevention) + zavegepant (Zavzpret intranasal 2023). dual indication acute + prevention 첫 small molecule.
3. **lasmiditan (Reyvow) 2019** = ditan first-in-class — 5-HT1F selective non-vasoconstrictor. CV-contraindicated (CAD/stroke/uncontrolled HTN) triptan-ineligible 환자 첫 acute option. quantum-VQE 의 5-HT1F vs 5-HT1B/1D selectivity 가 직접 fit.
4. **CGRP paradigm shift 2018-2024 + ditan/gepant/mAb 三-class 선택 framework** = 환자별 acute (gepant + ditan + triptan) + prevention (mAb + gepant + 기존 topiramate/propranolol/Botox) algorithm 변화. quantum-VQE 의 CGRP-RAMP1 PPI 표적 fit.
5. **onabotulinumtoxinA (Botox) 2010 chronic migraine** = PREEMPT 31-site IM injection — 만성 편두통 ≥15일/월 + ≥4시간 발작 only. SNAP-25 cleavage neurogenic inflammation suppression. quantum-VQE 의 large-protein toxin scaffold 한정.
6. **classical prevention 1차** = topiramate (Topamax 2004) + propranolol + valproate + amitriptyline + venlafaxine — 50+년 evidence. CGRP mAb 가 1차 표준 대체 못 함 (cost + access). algorithm 에서 CGRP mAb 는 2-3 classical 실패 후.
7. **triptan era 1992-2002** = sumatriptan 1992 부터 7-triptan family. CV vasoconstriction (ergot 유산) limit + 약물남용 두통 (medication overuse headache) 유발 — 월 ≥10일 사용 시. 5-HT1B/1D pocket vs 5-HT1F (lasmiditan) 분리 가 mechanism breakthrough.
8. **DHE (dihydroergotamine) 1946 → Trudhesa 2021 reformulated nasal** = ergot alkaloid 80년 약. status migrainosus + refractory 적응증. ergot 5-HT/α/D promiscuity = pocket VQE 의 multi-target 모델.
9. **non-drug device era** = nerivio REN 2019 (upper-arm REN) + gammaCore nVNS + sTMS mini + Cefaly eTNS — 임신/약물금기 환자 + 청소년 acute + prevention. quantum-VQE 적용 한정 (device biophysics).
10. **galcanezumab episodic cluster 2019** = first FDA cluster CGRP mAb (Emgality cluster indication 별도 승인). rimegepant cluster trial 실패 (gepant cluster 미달). cluster-specific CGRP mAb 가 mechanism 분리 가능성.

